{"type": "article", "id": 27029, "title": "感应式玩偶夜灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-19T07:13:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021440400R5VmDpW8krCwP1e.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>抱紧怀中的小动物玩偶，它就变成了一盏散发着温柔光芒的小夜灯，而在抚摸下它的光线开始慢慢变暗，最后又变成了普通玩偶的模样——这个名为 LeeLuu 的夜灯依靠拥抱转化为能量运作，由四位来自芬兰的女设计师共同研发而成。可爱的动物造型搭配讨巧的感应式设计，真的让人很想抱着它入睡。如果你也想在 LeeLuu 的陪伴下度过漫漫长夜，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/leeluu-the-magical-touch-sensitive-nightlight--2#/\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 69 欧元（包含邮费）。美中不足的是，它只能发往美国和欧盟国家。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144038IdU4WQ3ta6xpr1e9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214403879FaNwOXrQdiGKlb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144039p78sWAnDZoJNRE1q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63870968\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"dragged\" style=\"height: 275px; width: 375px; left: 505px; top: 1256px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144039UVthL1kabWBp9lGF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73225806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}